NAME: Advisory_Board
DESCRIPTION: An activity involving a group of experts retained to provide advice to BMS.

NAME: Cross_Org
DESCRIPTION: Activity Type used to prepare documentation only for an HCP to participate in a Cross-Org Activity

NAME: Exhibits_Booths_and_Displays
DESCRIPTION: An activity to rent floor space at medical or scientific events for communication and/or display of BMS or disease related information.

NAME: HCP_Sponsorship
DESCRIPTION: An activity where BMS pays, wholly or partially for hospitality and registration cost of HCPs  to attend Congresses or other Medical Events

NAME: Internal_Speaking
DESCRIPTION: An activity where a contracted individual(s) speaks to an internal BMS audience

NAME: Other_Consulting
DESCRIPTION: An activity to provide guidance or a tangible work product to BMS that is not in relation to any other activity listed here

NAME: Preceptorship
DESCRIPTION: An activity that provides an HCP with practical experience under the instruction of another HCP(s), typically in an institution setting.

NAME: R&D Committee
DESCRIPTION: An activity where a group of contracted individuals are retained by BMS to participate in committees in connection with a clinical trial (e.g. DMC, SSC)

NAME: Speaker_Meeting
DESCRIPTION: An activity where an individual(s) speaks to an external audience on behalf of BMS.

NAME: Speaker_Series
DESCRIPTION: A series of Speaker Meetings where an individual(s) speaks to an external audience on behalf of BMS.

NAME: Speaker_Training
DESCRIPTION: An activity to train individuals who are contracted to speak on behalf of BMS in subsequent speaker meetings.

NAME: Event_Purchase
DESCRIPTION: Event Purchases allow conducting a Speaker meeting, HCP Sponsorship & Exhibits Display all under one umbrella
